snippet.title: [GOTY 2012 #3] Best VGM 1270 - Guild Wars 2 - The Seraph
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 1203 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pxAH2U75BoM
Best VGM 1935 - https://youtu.be/f0bj_Aqhbb8

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

PC
Guild Wars 2
The Seraph (Eye of Zhaitan)
Jeremy Soule & Julian Soule
